title: Bug 130068[Regression]Report Parameter window doesn't pop up when preview a report with parameter.
description:
Description:Report Parameter window doesn't pop up when previewing a report with a parameter.
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the report.
2. Click Preview in Layout.

OB: Report Parameter window should pop up when previewing a report with a parameter.
EB: The Report Parameter window does not appear when previewing a report with a parameter.
SR: Fix the issue so that the Report Parameter window pops up correctly when previewing a report with a parameter.
